{"tid":2236564,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"巴基斯坦禁止境內人士使用中國短片分享平台TikTok。","createTime":"2020-10-09T14:26:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T14:59:08.000Z","uid":188515,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8e4774a83364762be1d3558c9ac0ca668290803e","tid":2236564,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T14:26:56.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】巴基斯坦宣布，禁止境內人士使用中國短片分享平台TikTok。 <br />\n<br />\n巴基斯坦電信管理局表示是因為收到不少投訴，指TikTok平台存在不雅或不道德內容，所以採取行動。當局已通知TikTok可以就禁令作申訴；在TikTok清除非法內容後，會再按機制檢視有關決定。<br />\n<br />\n巴基斯坦電信管理局上月24日，曾要求TikTok立即屏蔽巴基斯坦境內平台上的粗俗、不雅和裸露內容，並要求TikTok建立監管和審查機制，否則會依法採取必要措施。<br />\n<br />\n巴基斯坦的宿敵印度在今年6月，亦以保障國家安全和國民私隱為由，封殺TikTok等中國手機應用程式。<br />\n<br />\n巴基斯坦宣布禁用TikTok　指平台含不雅內容<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=408477&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D408477%26refer%3DShare&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzt%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=4f7e4046\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D408477%26refer%3DShare&h=6287782a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=408477&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"27511fc7f72a4c8954b93518cb005db6722192fd","tid":2236564,"uid":188515,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T14:27:46.000Z","msg":"說好的巴鐵好兄弟呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"941e89ce39c8c78c55d47fd6eb2e75fc4c6be810","tid":2236564,"uid":18724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T14:30:10.000Z","msg":"一邊聯署撐中國一邊禁tiktok係咩玩法?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f